comments.value: #User Story 13280 - Back Office Process for Registration

elements.name: Payment online for Registration as Small Breeder

steps.name: I am on SFWF Front Office Home Page "Chrome"
I Input Registered User's Username "Suraj" and Password "Admin@123"
I Click on Sign In button
I Verify Applicant's Successful Login
I Click on Register as Farmer
I Verify that User is directed to My Application Page
I Verify display of Farmers Card link
I Verify Programmes link
I Click on New Button to apply for Registration
I Verify display of Registration Type Page
I Click on Small Breeder Icon
I Verify display of REGISTRATION FOR SMALL BREEDERS page
I Select an Applicant Title "Mrs"
I Select Applicant District "Port Louis"
I Select Applicant Level of Education "Tertiary"
I Select Agricultural Activity "Full Time"
I Input Other Occupation "Manager"
I Upload Photograph "src\test\resources\Photo_upload.jpg"
I Verify for Photo upload success message
I Select No of years for Registration membership "2"
I Select Marital Status "Married"
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify Display of Particulars of Family Beneficiaries Page
I Click on Add Family and Beneficiaries
Verify Display of Particulars of Family Beneficiaries input table
I Select Family relationship for tea grower "Spouse"
I Input Family Surname "Keen"
I Input Family Other Names "Dafne"
I Select Family Gender "Female"
I Input Family Date of Birth "1Jan94"
I Input Family Occupation "Actress"
I Click on Beneficiary of life Insurance Scheme
I Click on Beneficiary of Accident Insurance Scheme
I Save Particulars of Family and Beneficiaries
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify Display of Livestock Activity
I Click on Add Livestock Activity
I Verify Display of Particulars for Livestock Activity Table
I Select Species "Cattle"
I Input Number of Male and Female "550"
I Input Total Heads "550"
I Select Reason "Meat"
I Save Livestock Activity
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify Display of Particulars for Cattle Page
I Click on Add Particular of Cattle
I Verify Display of Particulars for Cattle Table
I Input Microchip Number "AAA2563"
I Select Cattle Sex "Male"
I Select Cattle Age "1Month"
I Save Particulars for Cattle
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify Upload Required Documents Page is displayed
I Upload Copy of National Identify Card (ID) "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Existing SFWF Reg No (if any) "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload copy of Title Deed "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Copy of registered /Non-Registered Lease Paper "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Copy of title deed of land owner including cooperatives (for non-registered lease paper) "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Preliminary environmental report, Building and land use Permit and health clearance "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Location plan of farm including size "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload List of Tags Nos. (except poultry and pig) "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Animal Card DVs where applicable "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Verify for Document Upload Success Message
I Click on Add Additional Document
I Input Additional Document Name "Additional Document Test"
I Verify Success message for adding Additional Document Name
I Upload Additional Document "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Verify for Document Upload Success Message
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify Declaration Page for REGISTRATION FOR SMALL BREEDERS
I click on I agree to the Terms and Conditions
I Click on Photo checkbox
I Select Bank "ABC Banking"
I Input Bank Branch for Agro-Processing Enterprise "Port Louis"
I Input Personal Bank Account Number Agro-Processing Enterprise "0001252563636"
I Click on Submit Application "Yes"
I Verify Success message for application submitted for Small Breeders Registration
I Click on Cancel button not to proceed with another registration
I Verify Application Status "Submitted"
I Verify Payment Status "Pending"
I Copy Application Number
I Click on Shopping Cart for payment
I Select Application for payment
I Click on Proceed to Payment
I Click on Payment Icon
I Select Payment Method "Credit"
I Click on Final Proceed to Online Payment
